title: Bette Midler - For the Boys Soundtrack (Jazz) 1991 RESEED
description:
MP3/320kbps

For the Boys is the soundtrack to the feature film For the Boys. The album was released in 1991 and features Bette Midler, who also starred in the film. James Caan, who also stars in the film, is also featured on a couple tracks.

Producers: Arif Mardin, Mark Shaiman, Dave Grusin, Joe Mardin.
